Ready for more great food fun? Join us this Saturday at 10am PT for vegan food master Tal Ronnen as he discusses his new cookbook based on the recipes from Crossroads Kitchen. More into meat? We'll look at the rapid expansion of Shake Shack in LA as well.

We'll then sample more wine thanks to Wine Exchange, Meet a very unique food blogger and his blog Sherman's Food Adventures, and lastly, preview a benefit for a special OC chef being held at The Original Manassero Farms in Irvine.

All this and so much more. So join us LIVE this Saturday at 10AM PT on Angels Radio AM830!

Shake Shack crew working at 6:07pm in JFK airport rocks!!!!!! The airport wide credit card and cash systems crashed, the lines were long, but these guys hung in there and provided top class customer service!!! They rolled up their sleeves, put on their smiles, and began taking orders the old fashioned way! Broke out their calculators and the menu and an older machinery and cranked out the best burgers around!!! Please let this crew know how much we appreciate them!! Shakeshack JFK Shake Shack John F. Kennedy International Airport
